						<div class="postbody">The <a href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/PPU_registers#Mask_.28.242001.29_.3E_write" class="postlink">color emphasis, left column mask, and monochrome bits</a> can be changed at any time. The overscan isn't normally visible on the NES, and you can't change the palette midscreen without disabling rendering (and reenabling, and breaking sprites).</div>

